          "report": "I grouped the work into three execution batches: checkpoints-cleanup first to remove stale duplicate modules from production scope, shared-pbp second to centralize repeated play-by-play logic and normalize fetch/error behavior, and tests-and-contracts third to add annotations and regression checks around the new seams.",
